  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate PET-CT and EmII/3-10 serology as potential markers to
      assess the parasitocidal effect of benzimidazoles

        -  Trial with medicinal product
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
